<p source="SHANGBO.YOUHUANGJIANGQI 8.52.1 (STRIP 1A) MACHENGYUAN 8: 272 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-1a.1">有惶 (?)將起今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-1a.2">助 (?)余教保子今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-1a.3">使游於仁今兮, 【1B】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YOUHUANGJIANGQI 8.52.2 (STRIP 2) MACHENGYUAN 8: 275 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.1">[...]自悔今兮 ,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.2">有過而能改今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.3">無奉有風今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.4">同奉異心今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-2a.5">有奉 [...]【2】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YOUHUANGJIANGQI 8.52.3 (STRIP 4) MACHENGYUAN 8: 278 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.1">離居而同欲今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.2">周流天下今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.3">將莫惶今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.4">有不善心耳今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.5">莫不變改今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-3a.6">如女子將泣今兮[...]【4】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YOUHUANGJIANGQI 8.52.4 (STRIP 5) MACHENGYUAN 8: 281 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.1">[...]若余子力今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.2">族(奏蹴)緩緩必溪毋忤 (?)今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.3">日月昭明今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-4a.4">視毋以三誑” [...]【5】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YOUHUANGJIANGQI 8.52.5 (STRIPS 3, 1A) MACHENGYUAN 8: 277, 272 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.1">[...]大路今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.2">敦[周]葳[椒, 槭,檄]與楮今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.3">慮(?)余子其速長今兮, 【3】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.4">能與余相助 (惠?)今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.5">可期(冀)成夫今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.6">能為余拔[拜]楮極今兮.【1B】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-5a.7">[...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.YOUHUANGJIANGQI 8.52.6 (STRIP 6) MACHENGYUAN 8: 282 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-6a.1">[...]也今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-6a.2">命三夫之旁也今兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-6a.3">醪 (?)膰誘余今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-6a.4">囑命三夫兮.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-6a.5">醪 (?)膰之精也今兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0080_tls_001-6a.6">命夫三夫之請也今兮【6】</seg></p>

